{"tid":1590102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[發夢自保] 發夢前善用Telegram Schedule Message","createTime":"2019-09-23T14:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T12:13:39.000Z","uid":119806,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"236a3e7cb29f836f26feb11072a4003d5ef1e376","tid":1590102,"uid":119806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:33:15.000Z","msg":"近來狗隻捉到人, 會大聲吠、甚至用爪捂住被捕者個口, 唔俾佢講自己個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實只要用TG 嘅 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Schedule Message</span></span></strong>, 發夢果陣set 定個時間send 求救msg 去星火、612 或 熟絡嘅朋友, 咁就算你唔好彩俾狗捉左, 都會有人知道去救你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多人都知呢個方法, 不過都梗有人唔識, 我都講下啦<br />\n<br />\n步驟好簡單:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1</span></span>, 入Tg搵 <span style=\"color: orange;\">星火</span> 或 <span style=\"color: orange;\">612</span> 或你 <span style=\"color: orange;\">可信任嘅朋友</span>, 打好個msg<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KQyVWA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KQyVWA.png&h=12584bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2</span></span>, 長按 send掣, 按 Schedule Message, 就可以set 個時間寄出<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wnnp2BG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWnnp2BG.png&h=1e8b54e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRsNfWH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRsNfWH.png&h=cb1e9545&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3</span></span>, 每次發完夢, 你都知好多有需要嘅巴絲等人救, 如果你冇事, 就去delete 番個message, <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGO42B6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGO42B6.png&h=4d8e2b08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAbybvs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAbybvs.png&h=43edd6ee&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4</span></span>, 怕唔記得, 可以set 番個提示嘅, 最好就比Schedule message set 早半個鐘, 提自己Delete<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kqRY630.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkqRY630.png&h=a88bd724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/byYpiaG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbyYpiaG.png&h=62b3c2e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBpoyJ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBpoyJ0.png&h=7511aa6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yF714QF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyF714QF.png&h=13e449ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5</span></span>, 如果都係唔記得Delete 個Schedule message, 咁記得同佢地講番你安全喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">補充資料</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">星火</span> Tg: @Abccbbc<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">612</span> Tg: @ReliefFund612"},{"pid":"8a39fa72cf1eb67e808be90ccea516ee86f27cf9","tid":1590102,"uid":119806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:33:54.000Z","msg":"自推 (1/10)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85ea69147916f5449ce30ac58f5d417fca9137b","tid":1590102,"uid":293698,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:34:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"436f7e82f5047f4c6e2c1342d03d653ac2a5d020","tid":1590102,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"739bc5a9b4a7ca57c0210c81f27aaa3386747fa7","tid":1590102,"uid":119806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"自推 (1/10)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb854fbf6821235bcea7ead083041bc61984131c","tid":1590102,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"［行動post］10.1 維港悼念活動 燭光晚會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588919</a><br />\n<br />\n10月1日<br />\n晚上8點<br />\n維港兩岸<br />\n讓燭光燃點維港<br />\n悼念新屋嶺 &amp; 太子831 &amp; 運動中被逼害人士及死難者<br />\n<br />\n平反新屋嶺 平反831<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgm